  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nA user on Discord identified that Lighthouse will log `INFO Ready for the merge` even when Lighthouse itself is not synced.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nExtend the logic added in #3339 to take into account Lighthouse's sync status. We could add a new variant to the `MergeReadiness` enum like `BeaconNodeNotSynced` (and rename `NotSynced` to `ExecutionNodeNotSynced`).\r\n\r\nAlternatively we could just leave things as-is. Users running validators will see a lot of errors if their BN isn't synced and should know that this is an indicator that their node is _not_ merge ready.\r\n",
